high_descs: Walk forward and turn right before you reach the floor lamp.
Pick up the watch from the small stand in front of you.
Move left slightly to stand in front of the tall floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a watch by the dim natural light of a living room.

high_descs: Move forward toward wall, turn right to table with watch on it.
Pick up watch on round end table.
Turn left to wall then turn right.
Turn off lamp next to round table.
anns.task_desc: Pick up watch and turn off lamp.

high_descs: Walk straight towards the wall and turn right to face the small circle table next to the tall lamp.
Pick up the watch from the table.
Take a step to the left to face the tall lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a watch next to the light of a tall lamp.
